de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.gatt

Class BLE113lib

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.gatt.BLE113lib
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GattLibrary, PulseOximeterGattLibrary

    public class BLE113lib
extends Object
implements PulseOximeterGattLibrary
    BLE113 is a development board for bluetooth. A specific firmware is used in combination with the sensorplatform. The firmware forces bonding and encryption with authentication (passkey pairing). The pairing process must be done before using the sensor with the sensorplatform application. Furthermore, the firmware exposes a Bluetooth compliant pulse oximeter service with constant (fixed) data for SpO2 and puls rate. Only the mandatory fields are included, no optional fields.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka
